om/@ntv.de/video/7581482146263616790', description='Vier Köpfe, vier Themen, vier Meinungen: Bei "Blome & Pfeffer" wird heute wieder über kontroverse Themen gestritten. 🗣️ Clara Pfeffers Thema diese Woche: Die Regierung hat den Knall nicht gehört. Oder warum ist das Böllern an Silvester immernoch erlaubt? Darüber diskutiert sie mit Co-Host Nikolaus Blome, Buchautor Gabor Steingart und Grünen-Politikerin Franziska Brantner. 👉 Ihr seht unseren neuen Talk am 8.12. um 20.15 und um 23.30 Uhr bei ntv, ntv.de und Youtube. 👉 Oder, nach der Ausstrahlung, wann ihr möchtet, auf ntv.de, Youtube oder RTL+. #ntv #nachrichten #blomeundpfeffer', author='ntv.de'), VideoModel(video_id='7581114057168637206', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@britainbriefed/video/7581114057168637206', description='Putin Issues 72-Hour Ultimatum to UK – Starmer Faces National Crisis! #Putin #Speaker  #ReformUK  #ParliamentDebat #NigelFarage  #Parliament! #KeirStarmer  #primeminister #LabourParty #UKPolitics #Starmer #RachelReeves #PoliticalNews  #houseofcommons #LabourParty  #BritishPolitics #news #uknews #fyp #foryou #PMQs', author='britainbriefed'), VideoModel(video_id='7579766308510731534', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@maddowshow/video/7579766308510731534', description='New Gallup polling shows that Donald Trump is deeply unpopular with the American people, both in general approval and on specific issues. #fyp #news #politics #trump #poll @msnow', author='maddowshow'), VideoModel(video_id='7581627044451175693', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@msnow/video/7581627044451175693', description='During an unrelated Cabinet roundtable, President Trump appeared to deny comments he made last week, saying he would have “no problem” releasing video footage from the September 2 boat strike. Trump also lashed out at the reporter who pressed him about the previous remark, saying, “You are the most obnoxious reporter.” During the interaction, Trump also seemed to indicate that he had seen the footage of the boat strike. #trump #news #politics', author='msnow'), VideoModel(video_id='7581834559977737494', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@gandul_ro/video/7581834559977737494', description='Trump cere alegeri prezidențiale în Ucraina: „A venit momentul”. „Rusia este într-o poziție puternică de negociere”, spune Trump pentru Politico #trump #ukraine #zelesnky #news #gandul', author='gandul_ro'), VideoModel(video_id='7579637863214484758', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@ntv.de/video/7579637863214484758', description='Donald Trumps Kommentare über #Somalia und US-Bürger mit somalischen Wurzeln triefen vor Rassismus und Entmenschlichung. Entsprechend groß ist das Entsetzen bei Politikern außerhalb der republikanischen Partei. 📲 Immer aktuell informiert seid ihr mit der ntv App. #ntv\xa0#nachrichten', author='ntv.de'), VideoModel(video_id='7581850961556065566', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@foxnews/video/7581850961556065566', description='KAROLINE LEAVITT: “The Democrats are the greatest con artists in American politics.” “They are pretending to champion the issue of affordability when they themselves created the worst inflation crisis in a generation.” | @foxandfriends', author='foxnews'), VideoModel(video_id='7581815727246642454', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@itvpolitics/video/7581815727246642454', description='It follows the Ministry of Defence announcing the next steps in its Atlantic Bastion programme, which will aim to protect the seas around the UK from threats. #itvnews ', author='itvpolitics'), VideoModel(video_id='7581841747634916663', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@cnn/video/7581841747634916663', description="The Australian government says it has banned under-16s from social media for their own safety. Now, two teens are fighting the law in court, arguing a right to political expression. CNN's Angus Watson reports. #cnn #news", author='cnn'), VideoModel(video_id='7581363752688307478', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@official.politics/video/7581363752688307478', description='What is this ⁉️#viral 