 is this ⁉️#viral #unfreezemyaccount #shahbazsharif #maryamnawaz #nawazsharif ', author='official.politics'), VideoModel(video_id='7579710265609047309', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@newsweek/video/7579710265609047309', description='As #NATO foreign ministers gathered in Brussels, Secretary-General Mark Rutte said #Russia is "testing our deterrence," citing airspace violations, sabotage operations, and spy ships entering NATO waters as evidence of escalating hybrid threats. #newsweek #news', author='newsweek'), VideoModel(video_id='7581593181058387222', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@impuls_politik/video/7581593181058387222', description='Merz entschuldigt sich für die Stadtbild-Debatte #merz #politik #cdu #news #bundestag ', author='impuls_politik'), VideoModel(video_id='7580021426598464790', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@tagesschau/video/7580021426598464790', description='Schreibt eure Fragen an Bundeskanzler Friedrich Merz in die Kommentare! #arena #tagesschau #nachrichten', author='tagesschau'), VideoModel(video_id='7581456095168843030', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@dein_blick_/video/7581456095168843030', description='DAS ENDE DER DEUTSCHEN WIRTSCHAFT! Kolumnist Hans-Ulrich Jörges ist der Ansicht, dass die Regierung von Bundeskanzler Friedrich Merz nicht zu Reformen fähig ist #foruyou #deutschland #news #aktuell #breakingnews #viralvideotiktok #nachrichten #fyp', author='dein_blick_'), VideoModel(video_id='7581085997933317398', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@c4news/video/7581085997933317398', description="The Trump administration's new national security strategy is a 'giant middle finger to Europe', according to Ben Hodges, a former commander of the US Army in Europe. The document, released this week, slams European officials, accusing them of blocking efforts to end the war in Ukraine and appears to reassess the United States' long-standing alliance with the continent. #News #Channel4News #Europe #Trump #Politics", author='c4news'), VideoModel(video_id='7578570399827365142', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@focus_online/video/7578570399827365142', description='Putin spricht von großer Eroberung, die es gar nicht gab 🤦🏻\u200d♂️ #WladimirPutin fordert den #Rückzug der ukrainischen #Truppen aus dem #Donbass und droht damit, neue Gebiete militärisch zu erobern, sollte die #Ukraine sich weigern. Am Donnerstag erklärte er vor #Journalisten, dass die Zahl der besetzten Gebiete immer weiter zunehme. Um dies zu untermauern, berichtete er von militärischen Erfolgen in der Stadt #Komsomolsk. Das einzige Problem: Eine Stadt namens Komsomolsk gibt es gar nicht. Auf X wird #Putin für den #Fauxpas verspottet. #FOCUS #fyp #FOCUSonline #news #russland #ukrainenews #politik', author='focus_online'), VideoModel(video_id='7581442546606361911', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@dailymail/video/7581442546606361911', description="Elon Musk was left fuming at the European Union after it fined X $140 million, claiming the social media platform failed to comply with transparency rules. The EU claimed X was 'breaching its transparency obligations' under the EU's Digital Services Act. The compliance failures included the 'deceptive design' of X's blue verification checkmark, a lack of opacity regarding its advertising and a lack of access to public data for researchers. #news #EU #usa #X", author='dailymail'), VideoModel(video_id='7581725421469846839', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@cnn/video/7581725421469846839', description='In 2016, as then-presidential candidate Donald Trump vowed that US troops would carry out even his most extreme battlefield orders as commander in chief — some of which former military leaders said would be illegal — Pete Hegseth warned that service members had a duty to refuse unlawful orders from a potential President Trump.', author='cnn'), VideoModel(video_id='7581815146532605217', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@zdfheute/video/7581815146532605217', description='Die Fragestellerin ist Medizinstudentin aus NRW. Der Clip ist ein Ausschnitt aus der ARD-Sendung „Die Arena“, die gestern Abend lief. In der Sendung stellte sich Bundeskanzler Friedrich Merz den Fragen von Zuschauer*innen. Im Oktober hatte Merz in Bezug auf die Migrationspolitik der Bundesregierung gesagt: „[…] aber wir haben natürlich immer im Stadtbild noch dieses Problem, und deswegen ist der Bundesinnenminister ja auch dabei, jetzt in sehr großem Umfang auch Rückführungen zu ermöglichen und durchzuführen.“Die Aussage löste eine große Diskussion aus. Viele warfen Merz Rassismus vor. #merz #stadtbild #bundeskanzler #nachrichten', author='zdfheute'), VideoModel(video_id='7483708114584325418', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@msnow/video/7483708114584325418', description="Rachel Maddow breaks down some of the latest Trump administration headlines emphasizing that despite the dramatic news cycle, it's important to pay close attention to the lesser-known stories. “That is where they are trying to seize truly breathtaking authoritarian power…and the courts, for now, are kind of, sort of barely stopping it for now,” she states. #donaldtrump #pambondi #immigration #transgender #education #rights #doj #news #politics", author='msnow'), VideoModel(video_id='7581810708921191702', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@europe_pulse/video/7581810708921191702', description='Last Hours for Europe’s Peace Proposal #eu #politics #geopolitics #security #safety #donaldtrump #news #ukrainewar #putin #unitedkingdom #germany #france  Volodymyr Zelenskyy met UK Prime Minister Keir Starmer, French President Emmanuel Macron and German Chancellor Friedrich Merz in London to finalize Europe’s peace framework for Ukraine.  Kyiv wants the proposal completed by Tuesday evening before it is handed to the United States, which is exploring ways to mediate an end to Russia’s war. Zelenskyy made clear that Ukraine will not accept any territorial concessions.  After London, Zelenskyy travelled to Brussels for follow-up talks with NATO Secretary General Mark Rutte, European Commission President Ursula von der Leyen and European Council President Antonio Costa. The goal: keep NATO, the EU, and Ukraine aligned on air defense, energy support and the political conditions for any future negotiations. ------------------------------------------------------ *Subscribe to Europe Pulse* Stay updated with the latest news from Europe.', author='europe_pulse')]}
