 #trump #news #politics', author='msnow'), VideoModel(video_id='7581834559977737494', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@gandul_ro/video/7581834559977737494', description='Trump cere alegeri prezidențiale în Ucraina: „A venit momentul”. „Rusia este într-o poziție puternică de negociere”, spune Trump pentru Politico #trump #ukraine #zelesnky #news #gandul', author='gandul_ro'), VideoModel(video_id='7579637863214484758', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@ntv.de/video/7579637863214484758', description='Donald Trumps Kommentare über #Somalia und US-Bürger mit somalischen Wurzeln triefen vor Rassismus und Entmenschlichung. Entsprechend groß ist das Entsetzen bei Politikern außerhalb der republikanischen Partei. 📲 Immer aktuell informiert seid ihr mit der ntv App. #ntv\xa0#nachrichten', author='ntv.de'), VideoModel(video_id='7581850961556065566', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@foxnews/video/7581850961556065566', description='KAROLINE LEAVITT: “The Democrats are the greatest con artists in American politics.” “They are pretending to champion the issue of affordability when they themselves created the worst inflation crisis in a generation.” | @foxandfriends', author='foxnews'), VideoModel(video_id='7581815727246642454', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@itvpolitics/video/7581815727246642454', description='It follows the Ministry of Defence announcing the next steps in its Atlantic Bastion programme, which will aim to protect the seas around the UK from threats. #itvnews ', author='itvpolitics'), VideoModel(video_id='7581841747634916663', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@cnn/video/7581841747634916663', description="The Australian government says it has banned under-16s from social media for their own safety. Now, two teens are fighting the law in court, arguing a right to political expression. CNN's Angus Watson reports. #cnn #news", author='cnn'), VideoModel(video_id='7581363752688307478', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@official.politics/video/7581363752688307478', description='What is this ⁉️#viral #unfreezemyaccount #shahbazsharif #maryamnawaz #nawazsharif ', author='official.politics'), VideoModel(video_id='7579710265609047309', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@newsweek/video/7579710265609047309', description='As #NATO foreign ministers gathered in Brussels, Secretary-General Mark Rutte said #Russia is "testing our deterrence," citing airspace violations, sabotage operations, and spy ships entering NATO waters as evidence of escalating hybrid threats. #newsweek #news', author='newsweek'), VideoModel(video_id='7581593181058387222', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@impuls_politik/video/7581593181058387222', description='Merz entschuldigt sich für die Stadtbild-Debatte #merz #politik #cdu #news #bundestag ', author='impuls_politik'), VideoModel(video_id='7580021426598464790', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@tagesschau/video/7580021426598464790', description='Schreibt eure Fragen an Bundeskanzler Friedrich Merz in die Kommentare! #arena #tagesschau #nachrichten', author='tagesschau'), VideoModel(video_id='7581456095168843030', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@dein_blick_/video/7581456095168843030', description='DAS ENDE DER DEUTSCHEN WIRTSCHAFT! Kolumnist Hans-Ulrich Jörges ist der Ansicht, dass die Regierung von Bundeskanzler Friedrich Merz nicht zu Reformen fähig ist #foruyou #deutschland #news #aktuell #breakingnews #viralvideotiktok #nachrichten #fyp', author='dein_blick_'), VideoModel(video_id='7581085997933317398', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@c4news/video/7581085997933317398', description="The Trump administration's new national security strategy is a 'giant middle finger to Europe', according to Ben Hodges, a former commander of the US Army in Europe. The document, released this week, slams European officials, accusing them of blocking efforts to end the war in Ukraine and appears to reassess the United States' long-standing alliance with the continent. #News #Channel4News #Europe #Trump #Politics", author='c4news'), VideoModel(video_id='7578570399827365142', url='