g „Die Arena“, die gestern Abend lief. In der Sendung stellte sich Bundeskanzler Friedrich Merz den Fragen von Zuschauer*innen. Im Oktober hatte Merz in Bezug auf die Migrationspolitik der Bundesregierung gesagt: „[…] aber wir haben natürlich immer im Stadtbild noch dieses Problem, und deswegen ist der Bundesinnenminister ja auch dabei, jetzt in sehr großem Umfang auch Rückführungen zu ermöglichen und durchzuführen.“Die Aussage löste eine große Diskussion aus. Viele warfen Merz Rassismus vor. #merz #stadtbild #bundeskanzler #nachrichten', author='zdfheute'), VideoModel(video_id='7483708114584325418', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@msnow/video/7483708114584325418', description="Rachel Maddow breaks down some of the latest Trump administration headlines emphasizing that despite the dramatic news cycle, it's important to pay close attention to the lesser-known stories. “That is where they are trying to seize truly breathtaking authoritarian power…and the courts, for now, are kind of, sort of barely stopping it for now,” she states. #donaldtrump #pambondi #immigration #transgender #education #rights #doj #news #politics", author='msnow'), VideoModel(video_id='7581810708921191702', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@europe_pulse/video/7581810708921191702', description='Last Hours for Europe’s Peace Proposal #eu #politics #geopolitics #security #safety #donaldtrump #news #ukrainewar #putin #unitedkingdom #germany #france  Volodymyr Zelenskyy met UK Prime Minister Keir Starmer, French President Emmanuel Macron and German Chancellor Friedrich Merz in London to finalize Europe’s peace framework for Ukraine.  Kyiv wants the proposal completed by Tuesday evening before it is handed to the United States, which is exploring ways to mediate an end to Russia’s war. Zelenskyy made clear that Ukraine will not accept any territorial concessions.  After London, Zelenskyy travelled to Brussels for follow-up talks with NATO Secretary General Mark Rutte, European Commission President Ursula von der Leyen and European Council President Antonio Costa. The goal: keep NATO, the EU, and Ukraine aligned on air defense, energy support and the political conditions for any future negotiations. ------------------------------------------------------ *Subscribe to Europe Pulse* Stay updated with the latest news from Europe.', author='europe_pulse'), VideoModel(video_id='7581552750341721367', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@tracihogan5/video/7581552750341721367', description='The Blob wants Farage in Gaol #jacobreesmogg #ukpolitics #news #UKnews #UKPolitics #UKSociety #Explained #fyp', author='tracihogan5'), VideoModel(video_id='7581544767993957654', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@itvpolitics/video/7581544767993957654', description='Protestor interrupts debate on digital ID in Parliament #politics  @itvnews ', author='itvpolitics'), VideoModel(video_id='7579284006680726786', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@tagesschau/video/7579284006680726786', description='In Bulgarien sind Zehntausende bei regierungskritischen Protesten gegen Korruption auf die Straßen gegangen. Die Demonstration auf dem Parlamentsplatz in der Hauptstadt Sofia war die größte Kundgebung seit Jahren, die Menschen forderten mit Rufen wie „Mafia“ und „Rücktritt“ einen Regierungswechsel. #tagesschau #news #bulgarien #sofia #eu #korruption', author='tagesschau'), VideoModel(video_id='7581343969129303303', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@truthbombofficial/video/7581343969129303303', description='Reports say Russian submarines have arrived near Venezuela, creating new tension in global geopolitics. #Canada #CanadaNews #BreakingNews #Geopolitics #WorldNews', author='truthbombofficial'), VideoModel(video_id='7581829024989695287', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@newsweek/video/7581829024989695287', description='President #DonaldTrump called a female reporter "obnoxious" and a "terrible reporter" at a press conference at the White House, following a question about whether the full video of the Venezuelan boat strike would be 