ral #unfreezemyaccount #shahbazsharif #maryamnawaz #nawazsharif ', author='official.politics'), VideoModel(video_id='7579710265609047309', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@newsweek/video/7579710265609047309', description='As #NATO foreign ministers gathered in Brussels, Secretary-General Mark Rutte said #Russia is "testing our deterrence," citing airspace violations, sabotage operations, and spy ships entering NATO waters as evidence of escalating hybrid threats. #newsweek #news', author='newsweek'), VideoModel(video_id='7581593181058387222', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@impuls_politik/video/7581593181058387222', description='Merz entschuldigt sich für die Stadtbild-Debatte #merz #politik #cdu #news #bundestag ', author='impuls_politik'), VideoModel(video_id='7580021426598464790', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@tagesschau/video/7580021426598464790', description='Schreibt eure Fragen an Bundeskanzler Friedrich Merz in die Kommentare! #arena #tagesschau #nachrichten', author='tagesschau'), VideoModel(video_id='7581456095168843030', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@dein_blick_/video/7581456095168843030', description='DAS ENDE DER DEUTSCHEN WIRTSCHAFT! Kolumnist Hans-Ulrich Jörges ist der Ansicht, dass die Regierung von Bundeskanzler Friedrich Merz nicht zu Reformen fähig ist #foruyou #deutschland #news #aktuell #breakingnews #viralvideotiktok #nachrichten #fyp', author='dein_blick_'), VideoModel(video_id='7581085997933317398', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@c4news/video/7581085997933317398', description="The Trump administration's new national security strategy is a 'giant middle finger to Europe', according to Ben Hodges, a former commander of the US Army in Europe. The document, released this week, slams European officials, accusing them of blocking efforts to end the war in Ukraine and appears to reassess the United States' long-standing alliance with the continent. #News #Channel4News #Europe #Trump #Politics", author='c4news'), VideoModel(video_id='7578570399827365142', url='