Leyen and European Council President Antonio Costa. The goal: keep NATO, the EU, and Ukraine aligned on air defense, energy support and the political conditions for any future negotiations. ------------------------------------------------------ *Subscribe to Europe Pulse* Stay updated with the latest news from Europe.', author='europe_pulse'), VideoModel(video_id='7581552750341721367', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@tracihogan5/video/7581552750341721367', description='The Blob wants Farage in Gaol #jacobreesmogg #ukpolitics #news #UKnews #UKPolitics #UKSociety #Explained #fyp', author='tracihogan5'), VideoModel(video_id='7581544767993957654', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@itvpolitics/video/7581544767993957654', description='Protestor interrupts debate on digital ID in Parliament #politics  @itvnews ', author='itvpolitics'), VideoModel(video_id='7579284006680726786', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@tagesschau/video/7579284006680726786', description='In Bulgarien sind Zehntausende bei regierungskritischen Protesten gegen Korruption auf die Straßen gegangen. Die Demonstration auf dem Parlamentsplatz in der Hauptstadt Sofia war die größte Kundgebung seit Jahren, die Menschen forderten mit Rufen wie „Mafia“ und „Rücktritt“ einen Regierungswechsel. #tagesschau #news #bulgarien #sofia #eu #korruption', author='tagesschau'), VideoModel(video_id='7581343969129303303', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@truthbombofficial/video/7581343969129303303', description='Reports say Russian submarines have arrived near Venezuela, creating new tension in global geopolitics. #Canada #CanadaNews #BreakingNews #Geopolitics #WorldNews', author='truthbombofficial'), VideoModel(video_id='7581829024989695287', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@newsweek/video/7581829024989695287', description='President #DonaldTrump called a female reporter "obnoxious" and a "terrible reporter" at a press conference at the White House, following a question about whether the full video of the Venezuelan boat strike would be released. #news #newsweek', author='newsweek'), VideoModel(video_id='7581879023060454669', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@reuters/video/7581879023060454669', description='Reuters published around 1.6 million photos in 2025, capturing the personal and the political, triumph and tragedy, as photographers delivered news events and daily life from 150 countries to the world. #photography #news #pictures #reuters #journalism', author='reuters'), VideoModel(video_id='7579943760428092727', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@africa_factzz/video/7579943760428092727', description='Two powerful leaders, but the focus is on Poland’s President — a man known for protecting his borders, strengthening his economy, and staying disciplined in every aspect of life. His training, his strength, and his example reflect the old standard of leadership. Here is the question: Should modern leaders return to this style, where discipline and personal example matter as much as policies? #leadershipmatters  #strongleader  #polandnews  #globalpolitics #fyp ', author='africa_factzz'), VideoModel(video_id='7579597374176251158', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@skynews/video/7579597374176251158', description="Is a Reform-Tory merger on the cards? Sam and Anne discuss if it is practical and who could be driving it behind the scenes. Listen to Politics at Sam and Anne's via the link in our bio.  #SkyNews #UK #Politics", author='skynews'), VideoModel(video_id='7580420761270258946', url='https://www.tiktok.com/@tagesschau/video/7580420761270258946', description='Jugendliche protestieren gegen den Wehrdienst, Israel nimmt am ESC teil\xa0und ein betrunkener Waschbär randaliert in Virginia. Das sind drei News der Woche.\xa0#tagesschau #nachrichten #newsderwoche', author='tagesschau')]
